               <p>
                    Sara rents a post-hole digger from RentAll to build a fence. The cost is <m>$12.95</m> per day, 
                    and she keeps it for three days. How much will Sara pay?
                </p>
            </statement>
            <answer>
                <p>
                    <m>$38.85</m>
                </p>
            </answer>
        </task>
        
