        <exercise>
            <statement>
                <p>
                    Sara Nelson knows she will inherit <m>$10,000 </m>from her dying uncle within five months.
                     The bank will lend money at <m>4\%</m> simple interest. What is the largest amount of money
                    she could borrow now, if she plans to use her inheritance to repay it in five months?
